    <h2 class="text-black text-center text-md text-opacity-25 tracking-wide uppercase">Follow these steps to automate your sponsorships</h2>
    <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1">
      <div class="px-2 py-4 border-solid border border-black border-opacity-25 inline">
        <div class="mb-4 -mt-4 flex justify-between relative">
          <div class="text-black text-opacity-25">001</div>
          <div class="text-black text-opacity-75 uppercase">Add new Webhook</div>
        </div>
        <p class="max-w-sm mb-4 text-sm text-gray-800">
          Create a webhook with the values below for
          <a class="underline" href="https://github.com/sponsors/accounts" target="_blank">any GitHub account</a>
          that you would like to be sponsored for.
        </p>
        <div><a class="underline" href="https://docs.github.com/en/github/supporting-the-open-source-community-with-github-sponsors/configuring-webhooks-for-events-in-your-sponsored-account" target="_blank">Webhook for GitHub Sponsors Guide &rarr;</a></div>
      </div>
      <div class="px-2 py-4 border-solid border border-black border-opacity-25 inline">
        <div class="mb-4 -mt-4 flex justify-between relative">
          <div class="text-black text-opacity-25">002</div>
          <div class="text-black text-opacity-75 uppercase">Set the Payload URL</div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex space-x-2">
          <div>
            <code class="p-2 bg-black bg-opacity-75 text-linen">{{ webhookUrl }}</code>
          </div>
